column5: Cliff That old saw runs like new  Cut a few nights worth of campfire wood tonight in no time!  Anyone looking for small engine work , Cliff is your man !  thanks again. TB
Man the neighbour is gonna be pissed when he opens the curtains in the morning......
he works midnights might have woke him up !  TB

It was a real pleasure, those old saws are almost bullet proof, a little TLC and it will last forever. Just drain the fuel out of it and run it dry when you aren't going to be using it for a few weeks or more at a time.
